Package com.terturl.MMO.Effects

package com.terturl.MMO.Effects
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Effect
    Skeleton class for an effect to run
    FireProjectile
    Simple effect that will fire a projectile from Minecrafts basic projectiles https://hub.spigotmc.org/javadocs/spigot/org/bukkit/entity/Projectile.html
    JumpTo
    Ability that will cause the player to jump to near where the entity they are looking at is
    LineEffect
    An Effect that will shoot a straight line at an instant to the target point the player is looking at x blocks away determined by the EffectInformations range
    PullTo
    Ability that will pull an entity the player is looking at to near their location
    Sphere
    An effect that spawns a sphere with the offset away from the player
    VectorDirection
    A velocity based ability that will move the player in the direction they are looking
    VectorPush
    A velocity based ability that will push the player to a target offset from the player
    VectorRelative
    A velocity based ability that will move the player in the direction they are currently moving in
    WaveEffect
    Creates a triangle away from the player with the tip centered on the player moving out with each distance until the max range has been reached
  • Enum Summary
    Enum
    Description
    Effect.EffectType
    Repeating = The ability will run every x ticks for y amount of time Infinite = Will run until the player moves or takes damage Single = Run once Limit = The ability will fire x amount of times every y ticks
    Effect.LocationType
    Player = Location is based on player Point = Location is based at a point the player is looking at BLOCKAT/POINTPLAYER NOT USED
